{"id": "1394106398094397561", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 19, "author_id": "964125234871545886", "author_name": "red_rest", "author_bot": false, "content": "Woah I didn’t know that", "timestamp": "2025-07-14T00:01:06.550000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["289320818901778434"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1394105960645263391", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1394106680916054126", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 19, "author_id": "964125234871545886", "author_name": "red_rest", "author_bot": false, "content": "But u would know it’s bullshit if u have some knowledge of botanical biology. It is physically impossible for roses to bloom Blue. If someone said there’s a blue rose it means they either paint it, put blue dye in the water for rose to absorb the colour (and even then the colour isn’t really properly blue all the way and shade is more non blue then blue or something like that) or they’re just straight up bullshitting you", "timestamp": "2025-07-14T00:02:13.980000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-14T00:04:22.932000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "bow", "emoji_id": "1356053037159944473", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1394105950012444702", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1394107069820309636", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "507989103011168287", "author_name": "nightjar0928", "author_bot": false, "content": "There's a few ways to figure it out. In servers it's usually obvious since they post in every channel at the same time \n\nBut in dms it's trickier, there's usually signs though. Like the aforementioned ping thing. If you have other mutual friends you can check if they got the same message, and if they don't answer questions that's a good indicator (with the rise of ai though there's an increasing risk of them responding in a semi-believable manner)", "timestamp": "2025-07-14T00:03:46.702000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1394107375358709770", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "type": 0, "author_id": "507989103011168287", "author_name": "nightjar0928", "author_bot": false, "content": "Generally though, don't click links and don't download unverified files. \n\nJust because you know them doesn't mean it's genuine, if you know them irl, contact them through a different means of communication to check", "timestamp": "2025-07-14T00:04:59.548000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-14T00:05:11.448000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "bow", "emoji_id": "1356053037159944473", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
